# Executive Summary

This report presents the results of a microclimate analysis conducted for
**Tanger-Tetouan**, **Morocco**, generated on juin 14, 2026
using the **microclimAg** R package.

The analysis integrates:

- Land Surface Temperature (LST) from WorldClim + Open-Meteo
- Normalized Difference Vegetation Index (NDVI)
- Elevation data (SRTM 30s)
- Spatial clustering and statistical modelling

